the hobo's secret.

13:18.966 --> 13:20.431
Loren: That's it!
The wedding is off!

13:20.433 --> 13:21.833
I guess asking
your co-workers to plan

13:21.835 --> 13:23.702
the perfect storybook wedding
for free

13:23.704 --> 13:26.105
was a little too much to ask,
wasn't it?

13:26.107 --> 13:27.439
Thanks a lot!
Abbey: Shoemaker!

13:27.441 --> 13:29.508
Can you please just
book this band already?

13:29.510 --> 13:31.843
They're not gonna do it
without their dancing guy.

13:31.845 --> 13:34.713
I am the wedding planner,

13:34.715 --> 13:37.849
which means that I will do
everything in my power

13:37.851 --> 13:40.719
to make my special day --

13:40.721 --> 13:43.789
