of paternity leave.

13:47.861 --> 13:49.661
Fine!

13:49.663 --> 13:51.997
And tux!

13:51.999 --> 13:53.264
Oh, super-important
wedding question.

13:53.266 --> 13:54.800
If you were a wild dog --

13:54.802 --> 13:57.268
Where are the cans,
Fairbell?!

13:57.270 --> 13:58.337
♪♪

14:00.407 --> 14:02.307
