17:05.325 --> 17:08.661
Well, take it all in.
It's all for you.

17:08.663 --> 17:10.729
Most of these are
actually Jade's clients,

17:10.731 --> 17:14.132
but I cannot believe you got
Skaffirmative Action to play!

17:14.134 --> 17:16.201
Are you kidding me?
Yeah, you betcha!

17:16.203 --> 17:17.669
Listen, I know
this is last minute,

17:17.671 --> 17:21.339
but I would be honored
if you would be the best man.

17:21.341 --> 17:23.876
You mean I won the job?
You did. Above and beyond.

17:23.878 --> 17:26.678
Wow!

17:26.680 --> 17:27.946
No.

17:27.948 --> 17:29.214
What do you mean "no"?

17:29.216 --> 17:31.416
Hard pass.
Yes!

17:31.418 --> 17:32.684
[ Laughs ]

17:32.686 --> 17:33.952
So you're willing
to humiliate yourself

17:33.954 --> 17:35.420
as the dancing guy
in a ska band

17:35.422 --> 17:36.755
just so you could snub me
at my own wedding?

17:36.757 --> 17:38.490
Oh, 100 percent.
Yeah.
God.

17:38.492 --> 17:40.092
I guess you could
call it a long skon.

17:40.094 --> 17:42.360
[ Laughs ]
Is this about
the stupid bachelor party?

17:42.362 --> 17:44.697
You betcha!
Feels good.

17:44.699 --> 17:46.698
Well, I'd be lying if I said
I didn't see this coming.

17:46.700 --> 17:48.166
Mm-hmm.
Which is why I have
a backup plan.

17:48.168 --> 17:49.501
Oh, Scott!

17:49.503 --> 17:50.903
Pick it up, pick it up,
pick it up, pick it up,

17:50.905 --> 17:51.836
pick it up!
What's up!

17:51.838 --> 17:52.971
Looking skarp!

17:52.973 --> 17:54.172
It's best man right here!

17:54.174 --> 17:55.574
Yeah.
My best man.

17:55.576 --> 17:57.175
Seriously?

17:57.177 --> 17:58.443
Your name's Loren?
Yeah. Loren.

17:58.445 --> 17:59.745
This is my wedding.

18:01.916 --> 18:03.515
Oh, my God.

18:03.517 --> 18:04.983
My dad's here!

18:04.985 --> 18:07.920
Papa! Papa!

18:07.922 --> 18:09.654
I can't believe he came.

18:09.656 --> 18:11.123
He was against the wedding

18:11.125 --> 18:13.458
and everything else
I've ever done.

18:13.460 --> 18:15.327
Well, the love between
a skather and skon

18:15.329 --> 18:16.929
can be a beautiful thing.

18:16.931 --> 18:19.464
Is he sitting
on Jade's side?

18:19.466 --> 18:21.133
They're probably
just friends.

18:22.803 --> 18:26.005
[ Ska rendition of Wagner's
"Wedding March" plays ]

18:34.949 --> 18:36.882
