18:40.354 --> 18:44.022
[ Dramatic music plays ]

18:44.024 --> 18:47.559
Welcome, everyone.

18:47.561 --> 18:52.096
We are gathered here today

18:52.098 --> 18:57.302
beneath the piercing gaze
of Baphomet, the goat god,

18:57.304 --> 19:01.039
to celebrate the love
of two other little devils

19:01.041 --> 19:06.178
who played by their own rules --
Loren and Jade.

19:06.180 --> 19:09.047
But what can be said
about these two

19:09.049 --> 19:13.385
that can't be better said
through song?

19:13.387 --> 19:16.021
So, Dan, come on up.

19:20.394 --> 19:22.527
[ Audience murmuring ]

19:22.529 --> 19:24.997
[ Sighs ]

19:24.999 --> 19:27.599
