20:25.726 --> 20:28.727
Mission accomplished!
Am I late?

20:28.729 --> 20:30.929
You're right on time,
buddy.

20:30.931 --> 20:35.800
Loren and Jade have prepared
their own vows.

20:35.802 --> 20:37.602
[ Clears throat ]
Loren.

20:37.604 --> 20:41.473
Jade, when I first told people
I was marrying a prostitute,

20:41.475 --> 20:42.541
