Yes.

20:55.089 --> 20:56.889
But also on a personal level.

20:56.891 --> 20:59.091
I love you so much, Jade.

20:59.093 --> 21:00.358
Oh.

21:00.360 --> 21:03.027
Dark lord, preserve me.
[ Sniffles ]

21:03.029 --> 21:04.028
Good stuff.

21:04.030 --> 21:05.430
Thanks, bud.

21:05.432 --> 21:06.298
Jade.

21:06.300 --> 21:07.699
Loren,
I had my vows prepared,

21:07.701 --> 21:10.435
but then we spoke earlier,
and what you said,

21:10.437 --> 21:12.571
it touched me
deep inside.

21:12.573 --> 21:14.038
[ Audience cheers ]

21:14.040 --> 21:15.774
No, not like that!

21:15.776 --> 21:17.842
Like that,
but, you know.

21:17.844 --> 21:20.979
It made me realize that
you make me a better person.

21:20.981 --> 21:22.514
And I want to be
a better person for you,

21:22.516 --> 21:25.317
so I'm quitting
the escort game.

21:25.319 --> 21:26.985
Wait, what?

21:26.987 --> 21:28.853
What?
[ Audience murmuring ]

21:28.855 --> 21:30.122
Why?

21:30.124 --> 21:31.456
Well, seeing
how important it was

21:31.458 --> 21:33.258
for you to have this beautiful,
traditional wedding

21:33.260 --> 21:34.526
really touched me, Loren.

21:34.528 --> 21:37.862
It made me realize this kind
of life wouldn't be that bad --

21:37.864 --> 21:38.863
a normal life.

21:38.865 --> 21:40.065
Gross!
No.

21:40.067 --> 21:41.666
Who said I wanted
a normal life?

21:41.668 --> 21:42.935
Well, then, why would
you go through all this?

21:42.937 --> 21:44.269
For you.

21:44.271 --> 21:45.337
I did this traditional --

21:45.339 --> 21:48.340
mostly traditional --
wedding for you.

21:48.342 --> 21:49.541
Like the one
you always dreamed of

21:49.543 --> 21:51.276
during your terrible
childhood

21:51.278 --> 21:53.211
that led to a life
of prostitution.

21:53.213 --> 21:56.348
All the horror and agony --
Loren, stop.

21:56.350 --> 21:58.150
Loren, I didn't have
a bad childhood.

21:59.486 --> 22:01.886
The reason I got into all
of this was to pay off school.

22:01.888 --> 22:04.957
And then it turns out
I was just so good at it.

22:04.959 --> 22:06.158
"Was so good at it"?

22:06.160 --> 22:08.026
You're already using
the past tense?

22:08.028 --> 22:10.763
I can just feel my wokeness
drifting away right now.

22:10.765 --> 22:13.098
Well, is being woke
the only reason you're
in this relationship?

22:13.100 --> 22:14.699
No, of course not.

22:14.701 --> 22:16.368
It's like 70 percent.

22:16.370 --> 22:18.570
That's the most shallow
thing I've ever heard.

22:18.572 --> 22:19.972
Great.

22:19.974 --> 22:21.506
I can't marry you, Loren.

22:21.508 --> 22:23.308
What?

22:23.310 --> 22:25.109
You're breaking up
with me? Here?

22:25.111 --> 22:27.112
So, what, you're just gonna
run off down the aisle now?

22:27.114 --> 22:28.513
Well, actually,
do you mind if I stay?

22:28.515 --> 22:29.448
A bunch of my clients
are here.

22:29.450 --> 22:31.249
I've got big spenders
in the house.

22:31.251 --> 22:32.184
Fine!

22:32.186 --> 22:33.718
I guess I'll do it!

22:33.720 --> 22:35.320
[ Crying ]
No one look at me!

22:35.322 --> 22:38.557
Wait!
I need to release the doves!

22:40.661 --> 22:42.727
[ Audience gasps ]

22:42.729 --> 22:44.128
Oh.

22:44.130 --> 22:47.866
Oh, I forgot to cut air holes.

22:49.003 --> 22:51.170
Can I have these?

22:53.473 --> 22:58.943
[ Singing indistinctly ]

22:58.945 --> 23:01.079
Hey!

23:01.081 --> 23:03.281
Come on, man!

23:03.283 --> 23:05.017
Pick it up!

23:05.019 --> 23:06.485
Pick it up, pick it up,
pick it up, pick it up,

23:06.487 --> 23:07.886
pick it up,
pick it up, pick it up!

23:07.888 --> 23:10.889
Pick it up, pick it up.
Look at this asshole!

23:10.891 --> 23:12.957
Okay, you guys can eat
as much as you want,

23:12.959 --> 23:13.958
but then we're even.

23:13.960 --> 23:15.027
Deal?

23:15.029 --> 23:16.028
-Deal.
-Deal.

23:16.030 --> 23:17.962
Where's the Mac and Cheese
shooters?

23:17.964 --> 23:20.833
That's right. Tell me
I can't cater a wedding.

23:20.835 --> 23:22.434
You did a good job, Abbey.

23:22.436 --> 23:25.904
Thanks, Quinn.
I feel sorry for Jade, though.

23:25.906 --> 23:29.107
I have a feeling
she'll land on her --

23:29.109 --> 23:30.975
Whoo!
Oh!

23:30.977 --> 23:33.245
Well, she'll land.
[ Chuckles ]

23:33.247 --> 23:36.048
Anyways, it's a nice thing
you did for your friend.

23:36.050 --> 23:38.050
[ Singing continues
indistinctly ]

23:38.052 --> 23:40.519
Yeah.
For my friend.

23:41.655 --> 23:44.056
Wanna bend the anonymity rule
a little?

23:44.058 --> 23:45.524
[ Cellphone chimes ]

